---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="International Company Formation | ARM Management"
  description="Incorporate in 40+ jurisdictions across the EU, GCC, Asia, and Latin America. Legal entity selection to VAT registration — fully coordinated through a single ARM relationship."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507679799987-c73779587ccf?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Company Formation</span>
      <h1>International Company<br>Formation</h1>
      <p>Incorporate in 40+ jurisdictions across the EU, GCC, Asia, and Latin America. From legal entity selection to VAT registration — fully coordinated through a single ARM relationship.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">What We Do</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">One Relationship. Every Jurisdiction.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">Setting up a legal entity in a foreign jurisdiction involves far more than filing incorporation documents. It requires selecting the right legal structure, understanding local ownership rules, appointing appropriate directors, registering for tax, opening banking facilities, and ensuring ongoing compliance with local regulations — all while managing advisors who may speak a different language and operate in a different time zone.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">ARM Management coordinates the entire company formation process across 40+ jurisdictions through a single point of contact. We manage local lawyers, notaries, and incorporation agents on your behalf, translate and attest documents, and ensure that every step is completed correctly and on time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Services</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">The Full Formation Lifecycle</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1"><h3>Legal Entity Selection</h3><p>Advising on the optimal legal structure for your jurisdiction, ownership profile, and business purpose — LLC, branch office, holding company, free zone entity, or other structures.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2"><h3>Incorporation &amp; Registration</h3><p>Managing the full incorporation process including preparation and filing of constitutional documents, shareholder agreements, and all regulatory registrations.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3"><h3>VAT &amp; Tax Registration</h3><p>Registering for VAT, GST, corporate tax, and other applicable taxes in the jurisdiction of incorporation, including obtaining relevant tax identification numbers.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1"><h3>Director &amp; Secretary Services</h3><p>Providing nominee director and company secretary services where local presence requirements apply, including registered office addresses.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2"><h3>Bank Account Opening</h3><p>Coordinating corporate bank account opening in the jurisdiction of incorporation, leveraging our relationships with local and international banking institutions.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3"><h3>Ongoing Compliance</h3><p>Annual filings, confirmation statements, director changes, share transfers, and all ongoing statutory requirements managed on your behalf.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Jurisdictions</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Where We Form Companies</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇦🇪 United Arab Emirates</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Mainland, DMCC, DIFC, ADGM, JAFZA and all major free zones. Full lifecycle from entity selection to banking.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇬🇧 United Kingdom</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Limited companies, LLPs, branches. Full Companies House filing and HMRC registration.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇩🇪 Germany</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">GmbH, AG, and branch structures. Notarial incorporation, commercial register, and trade office registration.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇳🇱 Netherlands</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">BV formation, Dutch holding structures, and EORI registration for EU market access.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇸🇬 Singapore</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Private limited companies, branch offices, and representative offices. ACRA registration and MAS compliance.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇭🇰 Hong Kong</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Limited companies and branch offices. Companies Registry filing and Business Registration Certificate.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇲🇹 Malta</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">Ltd and PLC formation. Popular for EU holding structures and crypto/gaming licences.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇱🇹 Lithuania</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">UAB formation. Increasingly popular for MiCA crypto licensing and EU fintech operations.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇨🇭 Switzerland</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">AG and GmbH formation in Geneva, Zurich, and Zug. Swiss holding structures and commercial register.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇲🇽 Mexico</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">SA de CV and SAPI de CV. SAT registration and foreign investment registry filings.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇨🇴 Colombia</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">SAS formation. RUT registration and local bank account coordination.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3" style="padding:24px;background:#FDFAF6;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:2px"><h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🇵🇦 Panama</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.65">SA and foundation structures. Popular for international holding and asset protection.</p></div>
      </div>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:32px;color:#6B7280;font-size:15px;font-style:italic">Don't see your jurisdiction? ARM Management operates across 40+ countries. Contact us to discuss your specific requirements.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Ready to Incorporate?</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Tell us where you need to be established and we will give you a clear assessment of the optimal structure, timeline, and cost — before any work begins.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
